The paper deals with optimization algorithms for machine learning, specifically stochastic gradient descent (SGD) with delayed updates and compressed communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
